# Frontend conventions

- **No financial math in components.** Call `POST /api/calculator/plan` via `frontend/src/lib/api.ts`.
- **Types** mirror C# DTOs in `frontend/src/types/retirement.ts`; keep in sync when API models change.
- **Validation:** client-side in `frontend/src/lib/validation.ts` (per wizard step); server validates too.
- **FRA display:** computed from birth date (`frontend/src/lib/fra.ts`); read-only in Step 4 — do not add manual FRA dropdown.
- **Wizard:** `CalculatorApp.tsx` (5 steps), `WizardProgress.tsx`, `ResultsSection.tsx` (Recharts).
- **Styling:** global classes in `frontend/src/app/globals.css` (gradient header, green progress, cards).
- **Env:** `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` in `.env.local` (from `.env.example`); default `http://localhost:5051`.

Read `frontend/AGENTS.md` before changing Next.js APIs — this project uses Next.js 16.
